{"tid":1518842,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Now新聞台】：【關鍵一日】據報行會曾討論《緊急法》　視乎831情況再作考慮","createTime":"2019-08-30T11:15:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T12:52:29.000Z","uid":54824,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ef29897376f43213039526061a55cebf61d7087f","tid":1518842,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:15:57.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】即日新聞焦點：<br />\n<br />\n【關鍵一日】據報行會曾討論《緊急法》　視乎831情況再作考慮<br />\n<br />\n有傳政府考慮引用《緊急法》控制局面，據了解，行政會議曾循危害公眾安全的方向討論此條例，但認為坊間反響大需要小心處理，政府會視乎831當日衝突的情況再作考慮。<br />\n<br />\n另外，路透社引述消息指，行政長官林鄭月娥曾向中央政府提交報告，檢視回應民間五大訴求的可行性，包括撤回逃犯條例修訂，但遭中央政府拒絕。"},{"pid":"d11e9e4d01c70bd32daf96b27d157e5f7a96793f","tid":1518842,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:17:04.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831無大台 自行選地點<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUioL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=17ef6fab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 公海</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUioL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=7eef3a07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"